               <div class="tab_bar_panel">
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;"><a href="#FinancialSuitability">Financial Suitability</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#AccountDetails">Account Details</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#AccountSummary">Account Summary</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;"><a href="#TradingHistory">Trade History</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#BinaryHistory">Binary History</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#ForexHistory">FX/CFD History</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#BonusSummary">Bonus Summary</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive"><a href="#TradingStatistics">Trading Statistics</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_active"><a href="#ChangePassword">Change Password</a></div>
                  <div class="tab_panel_tab_item tab_panel_tab_item_inactive" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;"><a href="#AutoTrading">Auto Trading</a></div>
               </div>
               <div style="clear: both;"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tab_panel">
               <div class="change_password_tab_panel">
                  <div class="change_password_tab_content">
                     <div class="change_password_panel">
                        <div class="required_field change_password_required_field">* Required Field</div>
                        <div class="change_password_form_panel">
                           <div class="form">
                              <div class="formErrors"><span>Please complete all highlighted fields before submitting.</span></div>
                              <div class="formInfo" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;"><span></span></div>
                              <div class="field field_password field_textBox">
                                 <label for="password" class="label"><span class="field_required">*</span> Old Password:</label>
                                 <div class="collection"><input type="password" class="gwt-PasswordTextBox fieldWidgetError" id="password" maxlength="15" style="background-image: url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: 16px 18px; background-position: 98% 50%;" autocomplete="off"></div>
                                 <div class="fieldError" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">Enter your password<br>(5-15 characters) here.</div>
                                 <div class="fieldErrorIcon"></div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="field field_newPassword field_textBox">
                                 <label for="newPassword" class="label"><span class="field_required">*</span> New Password:</label>
                                 <div class="collection"><input type="password" class="gwt-PasswordTextBox fieldWidgetError" id="newPassword" maxlength="15" style="background-image: url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: 16px 18px; background-position: 98% 50%; cursor: auto;"></div>
                                 <div class="fieldError" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">Enter your new<br>password here.</div>
                                 <div class="fieldErrorIcon"></div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="field field_retypePassword field_textBox">
                                 <label for="retypePassword" class="label"><span class="field_required">*</span> Re-enter Password:</label>
                                 <div class="collection"><input type="password" class="gwt-PasswordTextBox fieldWidgetError" id="retypePassword" maxlength="15" style="background-image: url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-size: 16px 18px; background-position: 98% 50%;"></div>
                                 <div class="fieldError" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">Re-enter your<br>password here.</div>
                                 <div class="fieldErrorIcon"></div>
                              </div>
                           </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="change_password_panel_save_button_panel">
                           <div class="change_password_save_button">Submit</div>
                           <div class="change_password_save_button_loading" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;"></div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</div>
